      <RecitationInstruction>
         <ab>Y22.6a <em>āiiese yešti hāuuanə̄e</em> ...] <em>hāuuanə̄e aṣ̌aōne aṣ̌ahe raϑβe</em> [...] ʾytwn' cygwn PWN slwšdlwn' npšt' OD <em>aṣ̌ahe raϑβō</em> . <em>raϑβō bərəzatō</em> (Y22.21) 500, 510.</ab>
         <ab>Y22.6b <em>āiiese yešti sāuuaŋhə̄e</em> ...] <em>sāuuaŋhə̄e</em> cygwn npšt OD OL Y <em>dax́iiunąm daŋ́hupatōiš</em> (Y22.14) 88.</ab>
         <ab>Y22.6c <em>āiiese yešti miϑrahe</em> ...] <em>rāmanō x́āstrahe</em> OD <em>hāuuanōiš raϑβō</em> (Y22.21) 235.</ab>
      </RecitationInstruction>
