      <ab><em>miϑrahe vouru.gaōiiaōtōiš hazaŋhrō.gaōšahe baēuuarə.cašmanō aōxtō.namanō yazatahe rāmanō xᵛāstrahe aṣ̌aōne aṣ̌ahe raϑβe</em> = The standard <em>xšnūman Mihr</em>.</ab>
